This website provides personalized movie recommendations based on user preferences. Users can explore movies by genre, ratings, and trending lists to discover films that match their tastes.

Features
Browse movies by genre and popularity

Personalized recommendations based on user choices

Search functionality to find specific movies

Responsive and user-friendly interface

Installation
Clone the repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone <repo-url>
Navigate to the project directory:

bash
Copy code
cd movie-recommendation-website
Install dependencies (e.g., if using Node.js):

bash
Copy code
npm install
Run the development server:

bash
Copy code
npm start
Usage
Open your browser and go to http://localhost:3000 (or your configured port) to start exploring movie recommendations.

Technologies Used
HTML, CSS, JavaScript

React.js / Angular / Vue.js (adjust as per your stack)

External movie API (e.g., TMDB, OMDb)

